=head1 DESCRIPTION

For C<SCTE35_ENHANCED> output, defines a key and corresponding value.
MediaTailor generates these pairs within the C<EXT-X-ASSET>tag.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Key => Str

For C<SCTE35_ENHANCED> output, defines a key. MediaTailor takes this
key, and its associated value, and generates the key/value pair within
the C<EXT-X-ASSET>tag. If you specify a key, you must also specify a
corresponding value.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Value => Str

For C<SCTE35_ENHANCED> output, defines a value. MediaTailor; takes this
value, and its associated key, and generates the key/value pair within
the C<EXT-X-ASSET>tag. If you specify a value, you must also specify a
corresponding key.



